<p>Hello there,</p>

<p>This is to let you know that <a href="|project_link|">your entry</a> for <a href="<%= u.challenge_url(@context[:challenge], utm_source: 'hackster', utm_medium: 'email', utm_campaign: @context[:email_template]) %>">|challenge_name|</a> has been accepted. Hurray!</p>

<p>Please note that you have not won any prizes yet; this email simply confirms that your entry is eligible to participate in the <%= @context[:challenge].self_label.downcase %>.</p>

<% if @context[:challenge].in_progress? %>
  <p>
    You now have until <%= l @context[:challenge].end_date.in_time_zone(PDT_TIME_ZONE) %> PDT polish your write-up, fix bugs, and make it the best entry of all so you can win the <%= @context[:challenge].self_label.downcase %>!

    <% if @context[:challenge].winners_announced_date %>
      <%= @context[:challenge].winners_label %> will be announced on <%= l @context[:challenge].winners_announced_date, format: :long_date %>.
    <% end %>
  </p>
<% end %>

<p>Cheers,<br> The Hackster.io team</p>
